ce of more than a million people per year. </blockquote>\r\n\r\nFrom <a href="http://www.smm.org/about/history/" title="About the Science Museum of Minnesota">Science Museum of Minnesota Website</a>', 'Drupal Daze will be held at the <a href="http://www.smm.org/" title="Science Museum of Minnesota">Science Museum of Minnesota</a> in the <a href="http://www.smm.org/ltc" title="Science Museum of Minnesota Learning Technologies Center">Learning Technologies Center</a> on the <strong>second floor</strong> of the building. \r\n\r\n<h3>Directions and Parking</h3>\r\n\r', '', 1215131858, 2);
INSERT INTO `node_revisions` VALUES(47, 92, 1, 'Kyle Cunningham', 'My name is Kyle Cunningham and I''m a student of computer science and computer engineering at the university of Minnesota. I''m a free software developer and supporter and all around Linux guru. I am currently the webmaster at the Minnesota Daily, the University of Minnesota''s campus newspaper.  At the Daily I administer our numerous Linux servers, help troubleshoot network programs, program web (and desktop) applications and I am leading the initiative the redesign our website using a Drupal base. I enjoy playing video games, going out to eat, exploring and hanging out', 'My name is Kyle Cunningham and I''m a student of computer science and computer engineering at the university of Minnesota. I''m a free software developer and supporter and all around Linux guru. I am currently the webmaster at the Minnesota Daily, the University of Minnesota''s campus newspaper.  At the Daily I administer our numerous Linux servers, help troubleshoot network programs, program web (and desktop) applications and I am leading the initiative the redesign our website using a Drupal base. I enjoy playing video games, going out to eat, exploring and hanging out', '', 1215191054, 1);
INSERT INTO `node_revisions` VALUES(2, 93, 1, 'New Features in Drupal 6', 'This presentation will focus on highlighting the new features of Drupal 6.\r\n\r\nThough Drupal 6 has been out for about six months now, it still is not used in production yet.  This means that many people have yet to really see it first hand.  With the release candidates of CCK, Views, and Organic Groups just recently being contributed, Drupal 6 is starting to get to the point where we can see it being deployed in a production environment (without lots of maintenance).\r\n\r\nThis site is actually made with Drupal 6 and will use this as the case study.  We will look at the new core as well as some of the following modules that are significantly different in Drupal 6:\r\n<ul><li>CCK</li>\r\n<li>Views</li>\r\n<li>Devel</li>\r\n</ul>', 'This presentation will focus on highlighting the new features of Drupal 6.\r\n\r\nThough Drupal 6 has been out for about six months now, it still is not used in production yet.  This means that many people have yet to really see it first hand.  With the release candidates of CCK, Views, and Organic Groups just recently being contributed, Drupal 6 is starting to get to the point where we can see it being deployed in a production environment (without lots of maintenance).\r\n\r', '', 1215192991, 2);
