year. </blockquote>\r\n\r\nFrom <a href="http://www.smm.org/about/history/" title="About the Science Museum of Minnesota">Science Museum of Minnesota Website</a>', 'Drupal Daze will be held at the <a href="http://www.smm.org/" title="Science Museum of Minnesota">Science Museum of Minnesota</a> in the <a href="http://www.smm.org/ltc" title="Science Museum of Minnesota Learning Technologies Center">Learning Technologies Center</a> on the <strong>second floor</strong> of the building. \r\n\r\n<h3>Directions and Parking</h3>\r\n\r\nPlease see <a href="http://www.smm.org/directions/" title="Directions and Parking for the Science Museum of Minnesota">Directions and Parking for the Science Museum of Minnesota</a>. Metered parking is free on Sundays in downtown!\r\n\r', '', 1215579824, 2);
